</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-34_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-35_ pf-text-1"><strong>Cut </strong>- A break in the skin caused by a sharp object, resulting in bleeding.









</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-37_ pf-text-1"><strong>Graze</strong> - Surface damage to the skin, typically caused by a scrape against a rough surface, often with little to no bleeding.















